\section{Evaluation}
\label{sec:eval}
% ============================================================

\subsection{TT-OPD Results}
\label{sec:opd_results}

Table~\ref{tab:opd_trajectory} presents the validation accuracy trajectory for TT-OPD with EMA scheduling and cosine length reward (Sections~\ref{sec:opd}--\ref{sec:stability}). Starting from a 52.6\% baseline, the method achieves 61.1\% (+8.5 pp) at step 60, with a characteristic oscillating improvement pattern where each peak exceeds the previous one.

