\caption{TT-OPD training trajectory. Red: validation accuracy shows oscillating improvement, reaching 61.1\% (+8.5 pp) at step 60. Orange: response length oscillates rather than monotonically increasing, demonstrating the cosine reward's effectiveness in preventing response explosion. The dashed blue line shows standard GRPO without distillation for comparison.}
